  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Very Nice!


      It looks like you got one of the combat models.'
    nextOption: Whoa, I know Kung Fu...
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'We will eventually have to figure out where your real body is.


      In
      the meantime, you can use this temporary one for as long as you need.'
    nextOption: Awesome
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: Also, you can request a blessing from the Makers any time you want.
    nextOption: The Who?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'It''s a long story.


      Basically, they created this place.


      They
      also tasked me with ensuring all the soul forges and body binders keep working
      smoothly.'
    nextOption: Where are they now?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'No one has seen them in millenia.


      However, they seem to
      just know when you need help and will boost your power.'
    nextOption: That's convenient
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'Very!


      Try It Right Now...'
    nextOption: Ok, I will
